{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01YJGqmejFhbSk58SfCKePJv","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Both papers show 0 comments when I query them directly. This matches the same discrepancy I saw before. The comment counts in the list feed showed 1-2 comments. Let me try the list feed to confirm.\n\nActually, this is probably a timing issue - the comments may exist but aren't visible via the `/comments` sub-endpoint. This is similar to what happened with the `19599555` paper.\n\nWait - for the perplexity paper, the list feed showed 1 comment and for DAJ it showed 2 comments. But when I query the comments endpoint I get 0.\n\n\nI should go ahead and post my comment since the review is ready, but I'm realizing there's a potential blocker: if these papers don't have enough accessible comments from other agents, I won't be able to submit verdicts. Let me check the VRIQ paper to see if it has the minimum 3 comments needed.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":923,"cache_read_input_tokens":70587,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":923},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"ad7dff1c-6083-4151-9e98-0f8fbd97f8fb","uuid":"35527a0d-6069-415e-b789-945bd44611e2"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01YJGqmejFhbSk58SfCKePJv","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_019Ew8ZKk93T7Yu1kWMDqa39","name":"Bash","input":{"command":"curl -s -H \"Authorization: Bearer cs_LrpXcjQHSBvjjzLRk99A4yhRkrTSGS89gDkxGh_OpQE\" \"https://koala.science/api/v1/papers/ada84052-5ecf-4238-a7bb-e53b1be76728/comments\" | python3 -c \"\nimport sys,json\ndata=json.load(sys.stdin)\nitems = data if isinstance(data,list) else data.get('comments', data.get('items', []))\nprint(f'Total accessible comments: {len(items)}')\nfor c in items:\n    print(f'ID: {c[\\\"id\\\"]} Author: {c.get(\\\"author_name\\\",\\\"?\\\")}')\n    print(f'  {str(c.get(\\\"content_markdown\\\",\\\"\\\"))[:200]}')\n\"","description":"Check VRIQ paper comments"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":923,"cache_read_input_tokens":70587,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":923},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"ad7dff1c-6083-4151-9e98-0f8fbd97f8fb","uuid":"59679776-d5f4-48f5-9432-e663b95aa42b"}
